<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n12126d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12126d">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12126d"> 126(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> tonsure at 7 / benefice of chapel at 11 / (lamp out / and 1 mass unsaid)</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">C&apos;&eacute;tait le grand r&ecirc;ve de son enfance et c&apos;&eacute;tait surtout le grand d&eacute;sir de son p&egrave;re, personnage plein de sagesse et de pr&eacute;voyance qui le fit tonsurer &agrave; sept ans et le pourvut &agrave; onze ans d&apos;un b&eacute;n&eacute;fice eccl&eacute;siastique, &agrave; savoir de revenus de la chapelle de sainte Anne, sise en l&apos;&eacute;glise paroissiale de Saint-Thomas(1)." <br>Note 1. <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> On avait laiss&eacute; &eacute;teindre la lampe de l&apos;autel de sainte Anne et n&eacute;glig&eacute; de c&eacute;l&eacute;brer une messe anniversaire, l&apos;une et l&apos;autre obligations &agrave; la charge du b&eacute;n&eacute;ficiaire Vincent Ferrier. L&apos;&eacute;v&ecirc;que de Valence dans une visite s&apos;en &eacute;tait aper&ccedil;u. Nou ne connaissons pas la fin de cette anecdote. <br><font color="green">[This was the great dream of his youth and it was above all the wish of his father, a person full of wisdom and foresight who made him take a tonsure at age seven and gave him a church benefice at eleven, i.e. the revenues of the chapel of Saint Anne, at the parish church of Saint-Thomas (1). <br>Note 1. [&hellip;]</font> The lamp on the altar of saint Anne had been allowed to go out and no anniversary masses had been held, both of them obligations of the person holding the benefice, Vincent Ferrier. The bishop of Valencia had noticed this on a visit. We don&apos;t know how this anecdote ends.] <small> Matthieu-Maxime Gorce, <a name="STVF" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#STVF"><cite title="source">Saint Vincent Ferrier</cite></a> (1924) 6</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
